Now verify Equation 2 in this structure:
$y*x=h(x)$;
$y*(y*x)=h(h(x))=x$;
$x*(y*(y*x))=x*x=h(x)$;
$x*(x*(y*(y*x)))=x*h(x)=h(h(x))=x$.
Thus Equation 2 holds in every magma satisfying Equation 1. Therefore Equation 1 implies Equation 2.

